    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">For a good reference to learn C++ and understand how the program works under the hood, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Expert-proficient-programmer-learning-practices/dp/1838552650/" target="_self">see this book</a>.</p></div></div></div></section><?php include_once 'Elemental/footer.php'; ?>